A baller is someone who 'has made it to the bigtime' (ref. '''''ball''' players'') Now refers to people who are 'living it large.' In casual language, it is often replaced with "hella b", meaning "hella baller". Baller is a high compliment, and has taken on a meaning similar to "cool".

